data.description: Discover your perfect oasis in this meticulously maintained ranch home, offering 3-4 bedrooms and 1.5 baths. Impeccably decorated and updated throughout, with a versatile office/family room. Enjoy the serene landscaped yard with a spacious deck and a 2-car garage. Located near Sylvan Manor Park and close to lakes, parks, and shopping. Don't miss out—schedule your showing today and experience the charm firsthand!
